{"tid":1718935,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"協康會逾200人罷工抗警暴","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:28:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a3630b604da77ae5114fff48d0ef3cb443e579","tid":1718935,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:26:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191114/S4SKJVNYZFZDX43HZ7TJUUFP6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191114%2FS4SKJVNYZFZDX43HZ7TJUUFP6M%2F&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZJX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=e29511e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191114%2FS4SKJVNYZFZDX43HZ7TJUUFP6M%2F&h=bee7fa48\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191114/S4SKJVNYZFZDX43HZ7TJUUFP6M/</a><br />\n<br />\n協康會逾200人罷工抗警暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191114/large/1573663482_ce74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191114%2Flarge%2F1573663482_ce74.jpg&h=1871f1a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾200名協康會員工昨響應罷工，並以實名電郵通知行政總裁歐陽偉康。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】冷血政權縱容警暴肆虐，多間社福機構員工昨日響應三罷，其中協康會逾200人參與罷工，包括中心主任、社工、職業治療師及特殊學校教師等，更實名去信機構行政總裁歐陽偉康通知罷工，力陳政府及警察「不公義、不公平及非人道」，強調只因良知和履行公民責任罷工，呼籲機構勿忘初衷，「一起為公義發聲」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：余若薇哽咽：只求警守法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不滿政府縱容濫捕<br />\n<br />\n據悉，協康會轄下多間特殊幼兒中心及訓練中心等因罷工需關閉。歐陽偉康昨以電郵回覆員工時，以「不上班」取代「罷工」二字，引起員工不滿。<br />\n<br />\n救世軍社會運動同工關注組、基督教香港信義會社會服務部工會、東華三院員工社會運動關注組等均呼籲同工罷工，另有約140名來自不同社福機構、特殊學校等的執業言語治療師響應罷工。罷工聲明指警暴令人憤怒，政府一方面縱容警隊濫權濫捕，另一方面卻粉飾太平，「多月來生靈塗炭，已有多位市民犧牲或嚴重受傷」。facebook專頁「良言抗暴」成員黃小姐指出，警方強闖中大武力鎮壓，情況嚴重，業界紛紛自發罷工，發聲明表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n一群香港青年協會的學校社工則以個人名義發表聯合聲明，批評日前防暴警察肆意闖入多間大學校園，並施放大量催淚彈及橡膠子彈，導致多名學生受傷。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港演藝學院轄下三大學院（戲劇學院、舞蹈學院、舞台及製作藝術學院）亦分別有學生罷演或罷跳畢業作品，對政權表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王家文"},{"pid":"45cf76cadd9ffc2bba84a9af52a3c861cd3da9c6","tid":1718935,"uid":278228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感動"},{"pid":"5cd0db721dfafb0f470c01b6870aaf74d2418f70","tid":1718935,"uid":15228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45cf76cadd9ffc2bba84a9af52a3c861cd3da9c6","tid":1718935,"uid":278228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b75b814b70b292f8a4f5a009f629dd8c8d497d2","tid":1718935,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"a48b89ce1c742a7ddb5f9cb3cecde0de23e98ef4","tid":1718935,"uid":86774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:26:29.000Z","msg":"支持。"},{"pid":"3d4b614db98eb298485125a98027639e8034132f","tid":1718935,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27996904cd063f916e42cbc830503152a114518a","tid":1718935,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"3d40c6cd892eb3f1d61c94c9143d632cdbe9834a","tid":1718935,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:31:33.000Z","msg":"想入去做  有冇空缺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33ff00bf4de7f24ce370e3e073bb6143077f1fb","tid":1718935,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聲明 : 對於網上流傳有協康會老師鼓勵小朋友參與呼籲停止使用催淚彈一事，協康會特此澄清有關呼籲未經會方授權或許可而進行，會方將保留追究事件之權利。<br />\n本會所作之聲明純粹是因為擔心小朋友之私隱受到影響而發出。我們對有小朋友受催淚氣體而影響健康亦感到憂慮，期望政府以兒童福祉為最大依歸，避免任何兒童遭受傷害。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街,  仲要畀藍屍老屈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142a05b64e9f8c5bfd7aa8d9ff9ea666eb986085","tid":1718935,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:32:27.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01159a85f05c179d186e85b0ba362cf7fd7638b","tid":1718935,"uid":298778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"做開義工 十一月既活動都停哂"},{"pid":"ab31eac9309cd394c88c801da7f6439aa75dd6cc","tid":1718935,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a01159a85f05c179d186e85b0ba362cf7fd7638b","tid":1718935,"uid":298778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"做開義工 十一月既活動都停哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"風險太高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f4e3a97db491f1e6c759c461396e4c7c9201f6","tid":1718935,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"Very Good<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188efc2fefac3d3254e62f430792623a2e26a3f4","tid":1718935,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b3452658d67de3c74a04e25b93d5558da13a99","tid":1718935,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"夠吉士！"},{"pid":"e115c59bd7b0b069763b5d8146a90f6c0b1e750f","tid":1718935,"uid":290370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:40:15.000Z","msg":"終於有個有良知嘅機構<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66b9ac40b9f0a6efd458e9b2ae7cd01b0fd92ad","tid":1718935,"uid":86774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"一齊寫封信，感謝協康會響應罷工<br />\n<br />\ninfo@heephong.org<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主題：感謝協康會員工於11月13日響應罷工<br />\n<br />\n你好，本人是一名香港市民，從新聞得知協康會昨天逾200人參與罷工，包括中心主任、社工、職業治療師及特殊學校教師等，更實名去信機構行政總裁歐陽偉康通知罷工，力陳政府及警察「不公義、不公平及非人道」。本人感謝貴機構以行動向不義政府及警暴說不。<br />\n<br />\n貴機構一直都為有不同需要的人士服務，例如為自閉症、過度活躍症人士等等，提供治療及訓練服務。我們明白到，罷工一天，會影響兒童當日的訓練，對於機構來說，這是一個艱難的抉擇。可是，近日的警察暴力及催淚彈行動不但導致多人受傷，催淚彈的毒性亦嚴重影響兒童的健康。而且，更有智障人士於被補時被警察剝奪會見社工的權利、甚至懷疑被毆打。（註1）因此，作為支持兒童及不同能力人士權益的機構，實在有責任為此社會現象發聲。<br />\n<br />\n本人再次感謝協康會員工服務市民的精神。並希望協康會管理層，不會對罷工員工秋後算帳，並承諾保障其罷工的權利。<br />\n<br />\n註1:2019年10月12日，一名32歲中度智障男子周六晚上於旺角警署外被捕，被扣留超過二十四小時並被拒絕與社工會面。<br />\n<br />\n祝台安<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你個名"},{"pid":"c0a4a4743b3bc9fa100fe33ee1301c31ec1ed96a","tid":1718935,"uid":194560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2b0e78b373334d3c61cd045ae64413318d44a4","tid":1718935,"uid":86774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:47:39.000Z","msg":"一齊寫信感謝佢哋。<br />\n<br />\nfo@heephong.org<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主題：感謝協康會員工於11月13日響應罷工<br />\n<br />\n你好，本人是一名香港市民，從新聞得知協康會昨天逾200人參與罷工，包括中心主任、社工、職業治療師及特殊學校教師等，更實名去信機構行政總裁歐陽偉康通知罷工，力陳政府及警察「不公義、不公平及非人道」。本人感謝貴機構以行動向不義政府及警暴說不。<br />\n<br />\n貴機構一直都為有不同需要的人士服務，例如為自閉症、過度活躍症人士等等，提供治療及訓練服務。我們明白到，罷工一天，會影響兒童當日的訓練，對於機構來說，這是一個艱難的抉擇。可是，近日的警察暴力及催淚彈行動不但導致多人受傷，催淚彈的毒性亦嚴重影響兒童的健康。而且，更有智障人士於被補時被警察剝奪會見社工的權利、甚至懷疑被毆打。（註1）因此，作為支持兒童及不同能力人士權益的機構，實在有責任為此社會現象發聲。<br />\n<br />\n本人再次感謝協康會員工服務市民的精神。並希望協康會管理層，不會對罷工員工秋後算帳，並承諾保障其罷工的權利。<br />\n<br />\n註1:2019年10月12日，一名32歲中度智障男子周六晚上於旺角警署外被捕，被扣留超過二十四小時並被拒絕與社工會面。<br />\n<br />\n祝台安<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你個名"},{"pid":"1d2fb57faec149c56272cf166785d825e8e9415e","tid":1718935,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:50:01.000Z","msg":"工會呀"},{"pid":"44bf4cfd0eb6b4e9741d98a8f5fe2ef5bd29e602","tid":1718935,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6537e527046b841cb5edf355e669d721110e45c","tid":1718935,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:03:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8151ce6c995002fd48a4a12410ec03cca08debeb","tid":1718935,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f8dd88fbc3416b5d56d43c66b9c9d1681e0a85","tid":1718935,"uid":86774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲寫。"},{"pid":"06dff798087de57b3ec48f12549ebc0bb2469f31","tid":1718935,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}